  "description": "Replace the current content of /workspace/buz_customize_kanban/views/res_config_settings_views.xml with:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<odoo>\n    <record id=\"res_config_settings_view_form_inherit\" model=\"ir.ui.view\">\n        <field name=\"name\">res.config.settings.view.form.inherit.kanban</field>\n        <field name=\"model\">res.config.settings</field>\n        <field name=\"inherit_id\" ref=\"stock.res_config_settings_view_form\"/>\n        <field name=\"arch\" type=\"xml\">\n            <xpath expr=\"//block[@name='warehouse_setting_container']\" position=\"after\">\n                <block title=\"Kanban Display\" name=\"kanban_display_setting_container\">\n                    <setting id=\"kanban_warehouse_filter\" string=\"Kanban Warehouse\" help=\"Select warehouse to display available quantity in product kanban view\">\n                        <div class=\"content-group\">\n                            <div class=\"mt16\">\n                                <field name=\"kanban_warehouse_id\" \n                                       placeholder=\"Select warehouse to display in kanban...\"/>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"text-muted mt8\">\n                                <i class=\"fa fa-info-circle\"/> If no warehouse is selected, default warehouse will be used\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </setting>\n                    <setting id=\"kanban_pricelist_filter\" string=\"Kanban Pricelist\" help=\"Select pricelist to display product price in kanban view\">\n                        <div class=\"content-group\">\n                            <div class=\"mt16\">\n                                <field name=\"kanban_pricelist_id\" \n                                       placeholder=\"Select pricelist to display in kanban...\"/>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"text-muted mt8\">\n                                <i class=\"fa fa-info-circle\"/> If no pricelist is selected, the default sales price will be shown\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </setting>\n                </block>\n            </xpath>\n        </field>\n    </record>\n</odoo>\n```\n\nWrite exactly this content. No other changes.",
